•Duncan MightyMusician star, Duncan Mighty, alias Port Harcourt First Son, has been reportedly kidnapped in Owerri, the Imo State capital. “He was beaten and abducted by the gunmen amid gunshots,” according to an Instagram post this morning of Saturday, December 14, 2019, by his friend, billionaire club-owner, Cubana Chief Priest. Duncan Mighty was reportedly abducted after performing in Owerri. Details of the saga are till being awaited.